---
import Container from '../components/ui/Container.astro'
---

<section
  class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-black to-slate-900 text-white px-section py-20 overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/20 via-blue-900/30 to-cyan-900/20"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <div
        class="absolute w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400/30 rounded-full animate-float"
        style="top: 10%; left: 10%; animation-delay: 0s; animation-duration: 6s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-purple-400/30 rounded-full animate-float"
        style="top: 20%; left: 80%; animation-delay: 1s; animation-duration: 8s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-1 h-1 bg-cyan-400/40 rounded-full animate-float"
        style="top: 60%; left: 20%; animation-delay: 2s; animation-duration: 7s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-2 h-2 bg-pink-400/30 rounded-full animate-float"
        style="top: 80%; left: 70%; animation-delay: 3s; animation-duration: 9s;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-1 h-1 bg-green-400/30 rounded-full animate-float"
        style="top: 30%; left: 60%; animation-delay: 1.5s; animation-duration: 5s;"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div
        class="absolute w-64 h-64 border border-white/20 rounded-full animate-slow-spin"
        style="top: -10%; left: -5%;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-48 h-48 border border-white/15 rotate-45 animate-reverse-spin"
        style="bottom: -10%; right: -5%;"
      >
      </div>
      <div
        class="absolute w-32 h-32 border border-white/10 rounded-full animate-slow-spin"
        style="top: 30%; right: 10%; animation-delay: 2s;"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div
        class="absolute inset-0"
        style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 50px 50px;"
      >
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 opacity-10">
      <svg
        class="w-full h-24 animate-wave"
        viewBox="0 0 1200 120"
        fill="none"
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      >
        <path
          d="M0,60 C300,100 400,20 600,60 C800,100 900,20 1200,60 L1200,120 L0,120 Z"
          fill="url(#wave-gradient)"></path>
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="wave-gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
            <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#3b82f6;stop-opacity:0.3"></stop>
            <stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:#8b5cf6;stop-opacity:0.3"></stop>
            <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#06b6d4;stop-opacity:0.3"></stop>
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
      </svg>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Container class="relative z-20">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Descubre las experiencias únicas que FESTECH 2025 tiene preparadas para ti
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-4 h-auto">
      <div
        class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 md:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/20 to-purple-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/10 to-purple-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-1.avif"
          alt="Conferencias de expertos"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-8 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-200 text-sm font-medium mb-4"
            >
              Conferencias
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 leading-tight">
              Expertos Internacionales
            </h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Aprende de líderes mundiales en tecnología que compartirán las últimas tendencias en IA,
            Ciudades Inteligentes y Computación Cuántica.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-green-900/20 to-emerald-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/10 to-emerald-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-2.webp"
          alt="Talleres Interactivos"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[200px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 text-green-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Talleres
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Experiencia Práctica</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Talleres hands-on con las herramientas más innovadoras del sector tecnológico.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[200px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 text-green-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Talleres
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Experiencia Práctica</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Talleres hands-on con las herramientas más innovadoras del sector tecnológico.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="lg:col-span-1 md:row-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-900/20 to-pink-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/10 to-pink-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-3.jpg"
          alt="Charlas especializadas"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[400px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Charlas
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 leading-tight">Especializadas</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Profundiza en temas clave con expertos reconocidos mundialmente.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-3 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-900/20 to-red-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-500/10 to-red-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-4.webp"
          alt="Torneo de robótica"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[200px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-orange-500/20 text-orange-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Competencia
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-3">Torneo de Robótica</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Competencia épica donde creatividad e ingeniería se encuentran para crear el futuro.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-1 lg:col-span-2 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-900/20 to-blue-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500/10 to-blue-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-6.webp"
          alt="Muestra empresarial"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[200px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 text-cyan-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Empresarial
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Innovación Corporativa</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Descubre soluciones tecnológicas de vanguardia para transformar tu negocio.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-1 lg:col-span-1 group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-900/20 to-purple-900/20 backdrop-blur border border-white/10 hover:border-white/20 transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02] cursor-pointer"
      >
        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500/10 to-purple-600/10 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"
        >
        </div>
        <img
          src="/img/card-5.webp"
          alt="Museo Tecnológico"
          class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500"
        />
        <div class="relative p-6 h-full flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[200px]">
          <div>
            <div
              class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-indigo-500/20 text-indigo-200 text-sm font-medium mb-3"
            >
              Museo
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Tech Heritage</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs leading-relaxed">
            Un viaje por la evolución tecnológica.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
